for the sake of friendship.

24:24.726 --> 24:28.799
- What's that smell?
- What smell? I can't smell any smell.

24:29.486 --> 24:31.078
Camphor wood.

24:37.606 --> 24:39.995
Your guitar was made of camphor wood.

24:41.966 --> 24:46.118
It must have been worth a fortune.
Burn the soldiers right now.

24:55.446 --> 24:59.917
Look, there they are. Mush! Mush!

