Rimmer, there's something
I've got to tell you, something awful.

25:33.446 --> 25:36.961
If it's about finishing off the dog food,
I understand.

25:37.126 --> 25:41.802
- No, it's not about that...
- Hey! Hey! Hey! Oooooow!

25:42.006 --> 25:44.474
- Cat! Kryten!
- We made it!

25:44.646 --> 25:48.878
- Food! You brought food!
- So, where have you been?

25:49.086 --> 25:52.203
We rendezvoused with Holly.
When you didn't show up,

25:52.366 --> 25:55.676
- I said we should look for you.
- We've been everywhere.

25:55.846 --> 25:58.314
Fourteen moons, two planets.
I've been so worried,

25:58.486 --> 26:00.716
I haven't buffed my shoes for days.

26:01.566 --> 26:04.239
So, Holly navigated through five black holes?

26:04.446 --> 26:07.040
As it transpired, there weren't any black holes.

26:07.246 --> 26:10.204
- They were on the monitor.
- They weren't black holes.

26:10.406 --> 26:13.364
- What were they?
- Grit.

26:17.206 --> 26:20.562
Five specks of grit on the scanner-scope.

26:20.726 --> 26:23.081
