26:23.246 --> 26:25.237
and the thing about scanner-scopes...

26:25.446 --> 26:28.597
- Oh, shut up.
- Let's go.

26:28.806 --> 26:32.958
Something happened here, Kryten.
Something that made us closer.

26:33.126 --> 26:37.517
I saw a side of Dave Lister
that I never knew existed.

26:37.686 --> 26:42.157
He's not an irresponsible, selfish drifter,
always out for number one.

26:42.326 --> 26:44.794
He's a man. A man of honour.

26:47.206 --> 26:49.003
Excuse me.

27:10.366 --> 27:12.561
Open the trunk.

27:24.006 --> 27:28.238
Kryten, get the hacksaw and follow me.

27:28.406 --> 27:30.397
Where are we going?

27:30.566 --> 27:35.560
